Card/Details.aspx?name=Doom Blade\">Doom Blade</a> and <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Deathmark\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Deathmark\">Deathmark</a> sideboards. <br/><br/>No creatures in main deck. <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Back to Nature\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Back to Nature\">Back to Nature</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Naturalize\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Naturalize\">Naturalize</a>, <a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"War Priest of Thune\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=War Priest of Thune\">War Priest of Thune</a> and others of his Ilk are my main opposition, however the one card that completely shuts this kind of deck down is: <br/><br/>*drumroll*<br/><br/><a class=\"autoCard\" data:cardname=\"Leyline of Sanctity\" href=\"/Pages/Card/Details.aspx?name=Leyline of Sanctity\">Leyline of Sanctity</a><br/><br/>Back to the drawing ... <a href=\"javascript:void(0);\" onclick=\"ExpandPost(event, this, 90160)\">(see all)</a></span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"http://wizards.custhelp.com/cgi-bin/wizards.cfg/php/enduser/ask.php?p_prods=522,706,739&amp;p_cats=\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl05_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '90160'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy28052\">Stray_Dog</span>\r\n                                (7/27/2010 8:01:50 AM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r